reviewText: Out of all the items purchased, this is the most favorite and loved item.
This is a good price for the entire set.
My little cousin absolutely adores them. I'm glad he is able to experience what I loved as a child.
I watched these movies with my great grand son ,who loves everything dinasoir..we did have a glitch,the twelfth movie could not be played.overall we enjoyed them all very much
This was not a set.  It was a compilation of the releases put together and sold as a set.

I was not happy with the way I received this. It shows four dvds and I received 8. I chose this particular one because of the first being alone and 2-5, 6-9 and 10-13 being together. I received some doubles and some singles. I felt misled by the way it appeared on here.
